Epic 1: "Website Design and Functionality"

Description: This epic focuses on creating a website design that is easy to navigate and provides a seamless user experience. This includes implementing proper search engine optimization, ensuring the website is mobile-friendly, and integrating Google Analytics for user behavior tracking.

Goals:

Improve user experience on the website
Increase website traffic and engagement
Ensure website is optimized for search engines
User Stories:

As a website user, I want to be able to navigate the website easily, so that I can find the information I need quickly.
As a website user, I want to be able to access the website on my mobile device, so that I can learn on-the-go.
As a website owner, I want to implement Google Analytics to track user behavior, so that I can improve the website's functionality.
Dependencies:

Integration with Google Analytics
Website hosting and maintenance
Risks:

Technical difficulties with website design and functionality
Limited resources for design and development
Estimated Effort: 60 hours

Business Value: Improved user experience and increased website traffic and engagement.

Priority: High
